OL,3,CHow tiny tech is used to fight back
OL,4,Cagainst record Asian hornet numbers
OL,6,FFollowing a record year for Asian
OL,7,Fhornet numbers in Jersey, volunteers
OL,8,Fare trialling new technology to help
OL,9,Fthem find and track the invasive
OL,10,Fspecies.
OL,12,FOver 630 nests have been discovered
OL,13,Fthis season, more than double last
OL,14,Fyear's figure.
OL,16,FThey may be small, but keeping the
OL,17,FAsian hornet population at bay is a
OL,18,Fmammoth task.
OL,20,FOur frontline troops? A small but
OL,21,Fforensic army of volunteers.
