OL,3,CHow tiny tech is used to fight back
OL,4,Cagainst record Asian hornet numbers
OL,6,FThe number of Asian hornet nests found
OL,7,Facross Jersey in the last five years:
OL,9,FVolunteer Chris Isaacs has developed a
OL,10,Ftechnique that's halved the time it
OL,11,Ftakes to find a hornet nest.
OL,13,FIt involves putting out a bait station
OL,14,Fto entice the hornets, catching them
OL,15,Fand then attaching a silver streamer
OL,16,Fof reflective plastic onto the insects.
OL,18,F"It makes them much easier to see as
OL,19,Fthey fly back to the nests," says
OL,20,FChris, "So it helps with visual
OL,21,Ftracking."
