OL,3,CHow tiny tech is used to fight back
OL,4,Cagainst record Asian hornet numbers
OL,6,FTracking techniques range from the
OL,7,Fsimplistic to the futuristic.
OL,9,FIt doesn't come as a surprise that
OL,10,Fsome of the volunteers have a police
OL,11,Fdetective background: the latest
OL,12,Fequipment being trialled by the group
OL,13,Finvolves effectively 'bugging' the
OL,14,Fhornets.
OL,16,FA tiny radio tag is attached to the
OL,17,Fpests, who are then hunted down using
OL,18,Fdetection devices.
