OL,3,CHow tiny tech is used to fight back
OL,4,Cagainst record Asian hornet numbers
OL,6,F"We think it's going to speed things
OL,7,Fup completely," says fellow volunteer
OL,8,FJohn de Carteret.
OL,10,F"It's been calculated that it was
OL,11,Ftaking 25 hours to find a nest on
OL,12,Faverage. Reportedly, this system will
OL,13,Ftrack the nests in about an hour and a
OL,14,Fhalf."
OL,16,FBut finding nests is only half of the
OL,17,Fproblem.
