OL,3,CHow tiny tech is used to fight back
OL,4,Cagainst record Asian hornet numbers
OL,6,FThe hornet group are concerned that
OL,7,Fcuts to Jersey's Environment
OL,8,FDepartment budget will negatively
OL,9,Fimpact the island's ability to remove
OL,10,Fnests promptly when they are found.
OL,12,F"I think all the volunteers would like
OL,13,Fto see the nests destroyed quicker,"
OL,14,Fsays John, "We tend to get a bit of a
OL,15,Fbacklog.
OL,17,F"The ground nests are done pretty well
OL,18,Fimmediately, but the tree ones take
OL,19,Fthe time - potentially two to three
OL,20,Fweeks.
